title: El Gaucho Inca
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Beer/Wine, Peruvian, Argentinean, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A husband and wife run place that offers mostly animal meat-based Argentinian, Peruvian, and Italian food. But there are a few plant-based dishes and sides under the pasta, salad, and appetizer sections; and one veg choice from the Peruvian menu. Vegans need to specify.
